Author: bayareagoddess
Text: i’m doing is bad because we have an apple pie i haven’t made yet and ice cream and my mom keeps asking when i’ll make it but i’m too nervous i’m gonna eat it all :(  you’re not alone!!

Author: trashwitch420
Text: oh yeah i feel this BIG time  im moving home for 1-2 years to figure my shit out (mental health was so bad i failed out two semesters in a row, transferring to a community college, going back to therapy, seeing a psychiatrist, etc) and its so hard being at home. luckily my parents arent food pushers and im allowed to cook but like... i feel bad saying No to food because they get super concerned (about my depression) or no to eating breakfast/dinner with them for the same reason. and the snacks! everywhere! why tf do we always have to have good ass cheese, ice cream, and snack mixes stocked :((( i have to hide in my room just to get out of the kitchen. its so stressful :(   godspeed to us these next several months :/  ps ill add you on peach!! im arthroego
